title: Mi-Sex - Graffiti Crimes
description:
Graffiti Crimes was the debut album by New Zealand New Wave music group Mi-Sex, released in 1979. It reached number six on the New Zealand albums chart. The single "Computer Games" was the band's breakthrough, charting at number one in Australia.
